pbmeta:CellPac.Description: Individual 4 Pack containing 4 SMRTCells each containing 7.76 million ZMWs
pbmeta:CellPac.Name: Sequel II SMRT Cell 8M (4/tray)

pbmeta:ControlKit.Description: The Sequel Dev DNA Internal Control 1.0 contains a fixed template of 2 kb length bound to Sequel Dev Binding Kit 1.0 for use as an internal sequencing control. Reagent quantities provide spike-in controls for a minimum of 24 samples.
pbmeta:ControlKit.Name: Sequel II DNA Internal Control 1.0

pbmeta:TemplatePrepKit.Description: The SMRTbell Template Prep Kit contains reagent supplies to perform 96 automated SMRTbell non-size-selected library preparations of primer-annealed SMRTbell libraries for insert sizes ranging from 500 bp to over 20 kb. Reagents come in 4 x 24 reaction sets.
pbmeta:TemplatePrepKit.Name: SMRTbell Express Template Prep Kit 2.0

pbmeta:BindingKit.Description: The Sequel II Binding Kit 2.2 contains reagent supplies to bind prepared DNA template libraries to the Sequel Polymerase 2.2 in preparation for sequencing on the Sequel System. The result is a DNA polymerase/template complex. Sequel II Binding Kit 2.2 should be used only with Sequel II Sequencing Kit 2.0. Reagent quantities support 24 binding reactions.
pbmeta:BindingKit.Name: Sequel II Binding Kit 2.2

pbmeta:SequencingKitPlate.Description: The DNA Sequencing Kit contains a sequencing reagent plate with chemistry for single molecule real-time sequencing on the PacBio Sequel II with Dynamic Loading. Reagent quantities support 1 sequencing reaction to be used in conjunction with SMRT Cell 1Pac(s). (1 Cell max/Each Row supplies reagents for 1 Sequel SMRT Cell)
pbmeta:SequencingKitPlate.Name: Sequel II Sequencing Plate 2.0 (1 rxn)
